"13:34:2" : {s: 13, a: 34, w: 2, r: "عذب", t: "عَذَابٌۭ", l: "عَذَاب", lc: 322, tl: "ʿadhābun", lb: "শাস্তি, আযাব, দুর্যোগ ",e: "(is) a punishment", b: "আযাব", f: 77, rm: "chastisement, castigate, punishment, torture, torment, retribution, abstain/desist (e.g. from eating due to excessive thirst), relinquish, quit. To deny a thing, hinder anyone from, be inaccessible, prevent."},
